{"tid":2338841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕假得閒幫幫手填10mins問卷 有機會贏取100hkd","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T10:04:59.000Z","uid":381514,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65efa5b3f3d15e5323919dd31a75d2cb64515ebf","tid":2338841,"uid":381514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"大家好！祝各位聖誕快樂！我係香港大學主修心理學嘅final year 學生，而家做緊一份有關個人性格特質同網絡行為嘅研究，對象係18-25歲香港人，識得睇繁體中文，試邀你花10分鐘時間填寫呢份問卷，由於呢項係一項追縱性研究，問卷調查會進行兩次，第二次會係兩個月後send去email （預計係2021年2月尾到3月頭），成功完成兩次問卷嘅參加者將有機會獲取HKD100元正，每15位就有1位中獎。希望大家可以參加，聖誕放假得閒幫幫填下，唔會阻你好耐，感謝！ <br />\n<br />\n有關研究詳細內容可以scan 下圖嘅QR code 或者 Click 入去呢條survey link 到睇: <a href=\"https://qfreeaccountssjc1.az1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_55XkkdauVPsmAD3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqfreeaccountssjc1.az1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_55XkkdauVPsmAD3&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c13e89c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qfreeaccountssjc1.az1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_55XkkdauVPsmAD3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3p9M3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3p9M3V.png&h=806ee17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7acf008dc6c71869bd073c13f04ddae5614bb979","tid":2338841,"uid":175969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"善心打破〇回覆"}]}